long_description: Make it easy to load and transport your canoe by using these handy brackets on a Yakima car top rack (sold separately). Brackets cushion gunwales and prevent the canoe from shifting while driving at highway speeds. Includes tie-down straps to secure canoe to rack. Canoes and other long loads should be securely tied to front and back car bumpers as well as to the rack. Yakima Gunwale brackets only work on round and square crossbars.
